sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去到雅典真係唔識比錢搭巴士 就咁上左去又唔洗你比錢 但有當地人話比人捉到要罰幾十倍價錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa183a5e76d833a5c33d2a40cf12b5dac64d82dd","tid":43480,"uid":43735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T14:01:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Oia個日落睇足1星期都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁堅"},{"pid":"f734cd49ac0b72535b1c3564cb8642c0f2196422","tid":43480,"uid":13534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T14:02:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>santorini 行落去搭船條路真係好難忘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去到雅典真係唔識比錢搭巴士 就咁上左去又唔洗你比錢 但有當地人話比人捉到要罰幾十倍價錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個浸屎味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd68919b846fe9550843e920ecb9812dd1f35bc8","tid":43480,"uid":43735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T14:03:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>santorini 行落去搭船條路真係好難忘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去到雅典真係唔識比錢搭巴士 就咁上左去又唔洗你比錢 但有當地人話比人捉到要罰幾十倍價錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好多地方搭巴士會方便啲？"},{"pid":"fc42254eaf11adf318d88187e6d33b82c231ce12","tid":43480,"uid":13534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T14:03:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Oia個日落睇足1星期都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁堅</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n帶定腳架去<br />\n夜晚唔驚既出去睇星 夏天有銀河好狀觀"},{"pid":"b5f6b1d9b0020b9ee49e6d1ec34828ec35bea460","tid":43480,"uid":67879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T14:03:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴特農神殿呀 奧運果個場呀之類果啲<br />\n成個雅典好多歷史遺址多到數唔哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 印象中8成都係值得去睇<br />\n船飛我果陣係上網買定再自己print<br />\n果陣係去santorini, 倒塔咁早6點船 都要坐8粒鐘先到 我係貪平買慢船十幾歐 快船好似都要4粒鐘 飛機就一粒鐘唔使好似<br />\n果陣我係三條友去 3年前暑假去 撞正佢地破產冇耐好似<br />\n總之錢財唔好露眼就得啦 另一樣注意既就係佢地啲地鐵好少人查飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 果陣第一次去歐洲乜都唔識<br />\n見住啲人掂行掂過就有樣學樣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n搭船真係好耐 最後簡左搭飛機 45mins好似已經到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0089699677d378c8c4bb3a740b006d75fc69393","tid":43480,"uid":66759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T14:03:45.000Z","msg":"不錯哦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94b653d7bd34d65d3fed4d8436a645eea182541d","tid":43480,"uid":43735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T14:04:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Oia個日落睇足1星期都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁堅</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n帶定腳架去<br />\n夜晚唔驚既出去睇星 夏天有銀河好狀觀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知5月去有冇呢#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc"},{"pid":"43de1bcd109b1b089754cc2e157f2c0b99e39dbf","tid":43480,"uid":67879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T14:05:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>santorini 行落去搭船條路真係好難忘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去到雅典真係唔識比錢搭巴士 就咁上左去又唔洗你比錢 但有當地人話比人捉到要罰幾十倍價錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個浸屎味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一路避一路掩鼻<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 勁多隻騾仔衝上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61e45a9de492b404a01f28a802b5892d8a506dbf","tid":43480,"uid":13534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T14:08:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁堅</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n帶定腳架去<br />\n夜晚唔驚既出去睇星 夏天有銀河好狀觀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知5月去有冇呢#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n5月有啦 我個陣爬上屋頂影好正"},{"pid":"dcd5dffac081ff56e716817acaff53d145e5a62b","tid":43480,"uid":13602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T14:08:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>夏天去 熱死<br />\n巴特濃神殿必去<br />\n好宏偉 <br />\n佢d雲石椅即使烈日當空都係咁涼 好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幾年前8月幾去雅典，係熱到想死。<br />\n差啲中暑。<br />\n嗰邊係冇乜樹遮陰，地上啲石粒吸哂啲熱。<br />\n行幾行就冇乜心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我自己就鍾意santorini 多過雅典，<br />\n可能之前太有期望。因為去到好多都變咗做廢墟。加上太熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"967b1cf38dbe5c42597bf6e3581a7c1013ea9204","tid":43480,"uid":67879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T14:09:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>santorini 行落去搭船條路真係好難忘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去到雅典真係唔識比錢搭巴士 就咁上左去又唔洗你比錢 但有當地人話比人捉到要罰幾十倍價錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好多地方搭巴士會方便啲？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我個時住得辟D host教我地搭巴士轉地鐵 主要去唔同地方都係地鐵再尻行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d37a900b2b82f7a0a5a