好宏偉 <br />\n佢d雲石椅即使烈日當空都係咁涼 好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幾年前8月幾去雅典，係熱到想死。<br />\n差啲中暑。<br />\n嗰邊係冇乜樹遮陰，地上啲石粒吸哂啲熱。<br />\n行幾行就冇乜心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我自己就鍾意santorini 多過雅典，<br />\n可能之前太有期望。因為去到好多都變咗做廢墟。加上太熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMykonos都好似唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b28fa8186414c4937bc2f0e6ba112720fea6535","tid":43480,"uid":35878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T15:01:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁堅</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n帶定腳架去<br />\n夜晚唔驚既出去睇星 夏天有銀河好狀觀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知5月去有冇呢#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">祝用肥婆icon嘅人<br />\n身邊所有女性全部都係肥婆！！！<br />\n買美極買到破產！！！<br />\n<br />\n咁撚鍾意肥婆！睇飽佢啦！！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bg98YC0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBg98YC0.jpg&h=ba133c73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/19/221816_b711b6fe1d3b2b41c55bd3a640830968.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F19%2F221816_b711b6fe1d3b2b41c55bd3a640830968.jpg&h=9c4edbda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/96yYUN9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F96yYUN9.jpg&h=9e5db8d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/19/223517_37f626d9d14dcdba3ce3719da097170a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2